# React Query

Server state tek kaynağı. Her API resource için `useXxx` hook.

## Hook İskeleti

```typescript
export function useDigests(params?: DigestListParams) {
  return useQuery({
    queryKey: ["digests", params],
    queryFn: () => apiClient.get<DigestListResponse>("/digests", { params }),
    staleTime: 60_000,
  });
}

export function useCreateUser() {
  const qc = useQueryClient();
  return useMutation({
    mutationFn: (body: CreateUserRequest) => apiClient.post("/users", body),
    onSuccess: () => qc.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: ["users"] }),
  });
}
```

## Query Key Disiplini

`[resource]`, `[resource, id]`, `[resource, filters]` — invalidation granular.

## UI State Handling

| Durum | UI |
|-------|-----|
| `isLoading` | Skeleton (`S-LOADING-SKELETONS`) |
| `isError` | Türkçe hata + retry |
| `data.items.length === 0` | Empty state (`S-EMPTY-STATES`) |

## Cursor Pagination

`next_cursor` server'dan; `useInfiniteQuery` veya "Daha fazla" butonu.

## Anti-pattern'ler

- `useEffect` + `fetch` data loading
- Global mutation sonrası tüm cache invalidate
- 401'de sonsuz retry (refresh interceptor sınırı)

